<p>Here is an example of AppleScript:</p>
<pre><code>tell application &quot;Foo&quot;
    beep
end tell

&lt;div class=&quot;footer&quot;&gt;
    &amp;copy; 2004 Foo Corporation
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>
"""
		assert md_to_html(md) == html
	end

